{
  "stem": "19218.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "But even though the doctors were also inmates in there, there were actual physicians that were inmates.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And I remember what they have done.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "They have put on me a certain-- it's like a certain chain made out of metal or so.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And they had it connected.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "It was-- it had electricity to it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "And then they would probe my veins in my-- in my back someplace, and my neck.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "And every time they would hit a certain-- a certain part of it, you could see my fingers straighten out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "Like they would shoot electricity to it, and it would straighten out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "And after about three or four times, I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "This went away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "And of course, I was the happiest man on earth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "Then, just before the evacuation, it must have been January.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "I had some tremendous, very large boils on my back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "And they had to be drained.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "Of course, they had to be cut open.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "They just-- they just wouldn't go away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "And as I said, I was a clean fellow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "I was-- didn't matter, winter, summer, I would run.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "I would be the first one there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "Today, I mean, wintertime, I wouldn't dare go out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "And I would go out half naked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "I mean, I would run into the-- and this was quite a bit to run.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "I'd say it must have been about 300 yards to run to-- to the bathhouse.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "But I would do this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 95,
      "text": "Anyway, I was taken into the hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 96,
      "text": "And once you go to a hospital, of course, you lose your entire identity.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 97,
      "text": "You're no more of this barrack.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 98,
      "text": "So this barrack gets one piece of bread less, less soup, whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 99,
      "text": "It's now marked and whatever it is in there, I am now at-- at a hospital.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
